NB. m args : creates a gerund containing m verbs
NB. verb i fetches item i from the y argument
NB. ------------------------------------------------------------
args =: adverb define
  r=.>a: for_i. i.m do. r=.r`([:>i{]) end.
)
'`a b c d' =: 4 args

